info.author: John B. Cole, PhD
info.description: PyPedal provides an API that may be used to maniuplate pedigrees in a number of ways.  Key metrics include coefficients of inbreeding and relationship; effective founder and ancestor numbers; and expected inbreeding from a given mating.  If you have Graphviz and pydot installed, PyPedal can be used to produce a graph from your pedigree.
info.name: PyPedal
